Common.Highlight.Common.Text: In the heart of the Welshpool Industrial

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Welshpool Central is to become Perth's state of the art, high grade warehousing and logistics hub. Situated in the heart of the Welshpool industrial precinct, the property has been designed to accommodate occupiers with areas from 5,000sq m* to 22,180sq m*, available from Q4 2020* onwards.

Property features include:
• High truss 11m* internal clearance
• Two level office & staff amenities
• ESFR sprinkler system
• Four (4) recessed loading docks
• Eleven (11) on-grade roller shutter doors
• 10m Overhead canopies with sprinklers
• Dramix 3D fibre floors
• Energy efficient LED illuminated
• Concrete hardstand with double garrison fencing
• High volume power (4MVA), gas supplies & deep sewerage connected
• Large pylon signage
• RAV4 access
• Zoning ‘General Industry’

Positioned on a prominent corner site in the core industrial precinct of Welshpool, 11 kilometres* south-east of the Perth CBD, the site benefits from excellent access to major arterial routes including Leach, Tonkin and Roe Highways.

For further information or to arrange an appointment to discuss how the property can meet your specific business requirements, please contact the exclusive leasing agents.

*approx
